da128bfd","tid":1259151,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"有冇北漏洞拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a30bef6d29e43fd9dd49b28dcd4ed8764f88dc","tid":1259151,"uid":65906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7b88a986fe56e3304a06a7736873560ac8497ac","tid":1259151,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"日文都okay<br />\n印尼真係over左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD人即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"咁印尼係G20嘛"},{"pid":"d483048caefca6f640b55570b2ecab327b8dcf99","tid":1259151,"uid":41901,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"G20相關國家嘛"},{"pid":"98e8a08ca46ddbc7203b74fb08f23f1515c497c7","tid":1259151,"uid":73910,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:46:36.000Z","msg":"其實人地係講比G20既國家聽，唔係講比香港人聽（今晚集會目的都係請求G20幫助），咁印尼係其中一國，講印尼話有咩問題？<br />\n佢之後都有講德文、西班牙文、法文、韓文......呢d G20國家既語言呀"},{"pid":"37903baec9c1febc9f5d73e779e0a909b11667d8","tid":1259151,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c9e5a2467310c28246e3b26e18c4111da128bfd","tid":1259151,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"有冇北漏洞拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"北漏洞拉係共產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d60ef611d1da42582a2913ba5525cade37a8f2","tid":1259151,"uid":40287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:00:15.000Z","msg":"印尼啲私營媒體十分關心今次香港嘅事件，派咗幾十人去香港採訪。"},{"pid":"d43285cb2dbedaea883b1a339857fc77d0f544c7","tid":1259151,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8d60ef611d1da42582a2913ba5525cade37a8f2","tid":1259151,"uid":40287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:00:15.000Z","msg":"印尼啲私營媒體十分關心今次香港嘅事件，派咗幾十人去香港採訪。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:02:36.000Z","msg":"13哥講解下印尼人d勇武程度"},{"pid":"1f247a775aef4a7c2adfada55af6c220ec49cb31","tid":1259151,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43285cb2dbedaea883b1a339857fc77d0f544c7","tid":1259151,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8d60ef611d1da42582a2913ba5525cade37a8f2","tid":1259151,"uid":40287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:00:15.000Z","msg":"印尼啲私營媒體十分關心今次香港嘅事件，派咗幾十人去香港採訪。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:02:36.000Z","msg":"13哥講解下印尼人d勇武程度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:26:07.000Z","msg":"可能喺印尼人眼中，香港人冇勇武嘅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近印尼總統大選結果知道後，引發嘅行動，可以稱為暴動，有啲示威者可以稱為暴徒，真正嘅暴徒，除咗暴力，仲會四圍老笠放火，將成條街反轉。<br />\n<br />\n而好多企出嘅人，都有死亡嘅準備，好多寫埋遺書，嗰種狀態，係同黑社會冧友差唔多，所以最後真係死咗人。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係咪勇武呢？我都唔知，只知道，催淚彈，喺印尼每個月都會發射，印尼警察，對付衝擊者要開真槍，因為人哋實在太黐線，一把爪哇刀，將路邊樹木斬成枝狀，削一削前面，就變成武器，以前打日本仔，印尼人都係用呢啲簡單武器，近又得，遠距飛又得。雖然冇得打，但咁樣都可以插死唔少日軍，現時都係咁，但通常搽咗毒藥喺嗰頭到。<br />\n<br />\n相信香港黑警 vs 印尼暴徒，必須要出水砲。"}]}